2013-08-27 Julien Jorge <julien.jorge@stuff-o-matic.com>

	* Version 1.0.8

	* Fix the computation of the window's size. The game had no
	  graphics if the window was larger than the screen. Now the
	  window fits the screen and displays the graphics.

	* Fix syntax errors in .desktop files.

	* Fix various compilation issues:
	  - running-bear is optional.
	  - Port engine to Boost.FileSystem v3.
	  - Fix various compilation warnings.

	* Restore and update the scripts used to build the generic Linux
	  version.

2013-08-14 Julien Jorge <julien.jorge@stuff-o-matic.com>

	* Version 1.0.7

	* Restore keyboard handling in the game key field on Windows.

	* Fix various invalid memory accesses.

2013-07-14 Julien Jorge <julien.jorge@stuff-o-matic.com>

	* Version 1.0.6

	* The game is now open source.

	* The user can buy the game from any level of the demo. The full
	  game is unlocked by entering a valid key in the form of the level
	  selection screen.

2013-01-01 Julien Jorge <julien.jorge@stuff-o-matic.com>

	* Version 1.0.4

	* Bug fix: the textures were invalidated when switching the
	windowed/fullscreen mode.

2012-12-17 Julien Jorge <julien.jorge@stuff-o-matic.com>

	* Version 1.0.3

	* Packaging for Ubuntu

